<SYNC Start=40094><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=40096><P Class=ENCC>
If you want my advice,<br>you should take advantage
<SYNC Start=42196><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=42198><P Class=ENCC>
