<SYNC Start=46267><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46269><P Class=ENCC>
Escaping elaborate restraints,<br>for example.
<SYNC Start=49069><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=49071><P Class=ENCC>
If that doesn't bother you, then<br>why did you choose an activity
