<SYNC Start=66320><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=68758><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah.
<SYNC Start=70157><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=70159><P Class=ENCC>
You can safely resume<br>your nightly rituals.
<SYNC Start=72826><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79735><P Class=ENCC>
Could...
<SYNC Start=81268><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=81270><P Class=ENCC>
No, that's not...
<SYNC Start=83470><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84340><P Class=ENCC>
????
<SYNC Start=85839><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85841><P Class=ENCC>
Nature provides us<br>with so many wonders.
<SYNC Start=89176><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=89178><P Class=ENCC>
