<SYNC Start=93113><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=93115><P Class=ENCC>
Psilocybin.
<SYNC Start=95649><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95651><P Class=ENCC>
A naturally-occurring compound
<SYNC Start=97618><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=97620><P Class=ENCC>
