<SYNC Start=140194><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=140196><P Class=ENCC>
That is my oaf<br>of a neighbor.
<SYNC Start=142763><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142765><P Class=ENCC>
