<SYNC Start=2431915><P Class=ENCC>
Hi.
<SYNC Start=2433281><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2433283><P Class=ENCC>
I take it you<br>got my offer.
<SYNC Start=2434783><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2434785><P Class=ENCC>
