<SYNC Start=2437719><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2437721><P Class=ENCC>
Bearing gifts, actually.
<SYNC Start=2439187><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2439189><P Class=ENCC>
If you can<br>prove arson,
<SYNC Start=2441723><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2441725><P Class=ENCC>
you should be able to collect<br>insurance for the fire.
<SYNC Start=2444926><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2444928><P Class=ENCC>
So... this should do it.
<SYNC Start=2447229><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2447231><P Class=ENCC>
Pictures of a van?
<SYNC Start=2450465><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2450467><P Class=ENCC>
Captured by<br>our security cameras.
<SYNC Start=2452467><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2452469><P Class=ENCC>
This van was parked<br>outside our brownstone
<SYNC Start=2454636><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2454638><P Class=ENCC>
a few hours before the fire,<br>when your guests were out.
<SYNC Start=2457072><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2457074><P Class=ENCC>
But no one in the neighborhood<br>hired an electrician that day.
<SYNC Start=2460742><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2460744><P Class=ENCC>
And in fact, this electrician<br>works almost exclusively
<SYNC Start=2463478><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2463480><P Class=ENCC>
