<SYNC Start=2472487><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2472489><P Class=ENCC>
Yesterday he tried again.
<SYNC Start=2474356><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2474358><P Class=ENCC>
He said that your fire proved
<SYNC Start=2476591><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2476593><P Class=ENCC>
that AwayKays were<br>unsafe and underinsured.
<SYNC Start=2478660><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2478662><P Class=ENCC>
He hired an electrician<br>to start the fire?
<SYNC Start=2482631><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2482633><P Class=ENCC>
I spoke to<br>the arson investigators.
<SYNC Start=2485200><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2485202><P Class=ENCC>
The electrician is in custody,
<SYNC Start=2487002><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2487004><P Class=ENCC>
