<SYNC Start=2490172><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2490174><P Class=ENCC>
Well, if I get an<br>insurance settlement,
<SYNC Start=2492407><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2492409><P Class=ENCC>
