<SYNC Start=2499681><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2500918><P Class=ENCC>
Robert Frost said that fences<br>make good neighbors.
<SYNC Start=2504920><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2504922><P Class=ENCC>
But maybe that's<br>because there wasn't
<SYNC Start=2507322><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2507324><P Class=ENCC>
sound-dampening<br>insulation back then.
<SYNC Start=2509825><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2509827><P Class=ENCC>
Since you are rebuilding anyway,<br>we can have it installed for you
<SYNC Start=2514196><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2514198><P Class=ENCC>
