<SYNC Start=2521670><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2521672><P Class=ENCC>
You don't even know me.
<SYNC Start=2523171><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2523173><P Class=ENCC>
We'd like to.
<SYNC Start=2525273><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2525275><P Class=ENCC>
All right.
<SYNC Start=2528243><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2528245><P Class=ENCC>
